    {
      "text": "SQLite database initialization: Use Python's sqlite3 module directly (CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS) rather than shell commands like 'sqlite3 < schema.sql'. Shell approach can leave empty DB files causing 'no such table' errors.",
